name: V_EHI_CLP_FILTER_RESEARCH
description: Contains information associated with a claim print record used for research enrollment-level EHI export filtering.

columns.name: CLAIM_PRINT_ID
columns.description: The ID of the claim record associated with a single hospital liability bucket.

columns.name: LINE
columns.description: The line number of the research enrollment record associated with the claim print record. One claim print record can have multiple associated research enrollment records.
